doctype html
head
    // Required meta tags
    meta(charset='utf-8')
    meta(name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no')
    // Bootstrap CSS
    link(rel='stylesheet' href='https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.4.1/css/bootstrap.min.css' integrity='sha384-Vkoo8x4CGsO3+Hhxv8T/Q5PaXtkKtu6ug5TOeNV6gBiFeWPGFN9MuhOf23Q9Ifjh' crossorigin='anonymous')
    link(rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/payment.css')
    link(rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/logged_in_navbar.css')
    script(src='https://kit.fontawesome.com/2354c028ce.js' crossorigin='anonymous')
    title Payment

include logged_in_navbar
main.main.header-with-image.row
    section.main-welcome.col
        .main-img.pl-4.pt-5
            img.img-fluid(src='/images/logo.png' alt='logo')
        .main-heading
            h1.main-heading_title
                | Transfer Money Across World In Real Time With No Change
            p.main-heading_text.mt-3
                |
    .main-transfer-form.col
        .transfer-form.rounded.shadow-lg
            h3 Send Money
            form#form_1.mt-4(action='/payment/createPayment' method="post")
                .form_1
                    label(for='sendAmount') Send Amount
                    .input-group.mb-3
                        .input-group-prepend
                            span.input-group-text &pound;
                        input.form-control#sendAmount(type='text' placeholder='£1,000' name="amount-to-send")
                    .form-group
                        label(for='transferPurpose') Transfer purpose
                        p Prediction:
                        p#micro-out-div Predicting...
                        select#transferPurpose.form-control(name="transfer-purpose")
                            option General
                            option Family/Friends
                            option Groceries
                            option Shopping
                            option Bills
                            option Eating Out
                            option Entertainment
                            option Finances
                            option Transport
                            option Gift
                            option Holidays
                            option Personal care
                            option Charity
                    .form-check
                        input.form-check-input#savings-pot-check(type="checkbox" value="")
                        label.form-check-label(for="savings-pot-check") Round to savings pot
                .form_2
                    .form-group
                        label(for='sendingAccount') Account to send from
                        select#sendingAccount.form-control(name="sending-account")
                    .form-group
                        label(for='receivingAccount') Receiving Account Number
                        input.form-control#receivingAccount(type='text' placeholder='23242234454' name="account-number")

                .form_3
                    .form-group.mb-3
                        label(for='passCode') One time passcode (Please check your email)
                        input.form-control#passCode( type='text' placeholder='' name="one-time-passcode")
                button.btn.btn-lg.mt-4.btn-continue Continue Transfer
            .success-message
                h1.text-center.text-success.pt-5 Transfer completed
section.our-features
    .row
        .col-5
            .our-features_text
                h1.mb-4 Our Features
                h5 Transfer Money in a Minute with Secure Way
                p.text-muted.my-4
                    |
                p.text-muted
                    |
        .col-7
            .row
                .ml-5.col
                    .feature-card.shadow
                        i.fas.fa-shield-alt
                        h4.my-3 Fully Encrypted
                        p.d-none.d-lg-block
                            | Every payment can only be made once it has been encrypted to stop any payment interceptions where only we can can decrypt it.
                .col
                    .feature-card.shadow
                        i.far.fa-id-card
                        h4.my-3 24/7 Services
                        p.d-none.d-lg-block
                            | We offer 24/7 services so no customer has to worry at any time of the day
            .row
                .ml-5.col
                    .feature-card.shadow
                        i.fas.fa-user-shield
                        h4.my-3 Safe And Secure
                        p.d-none.d-lg-block
                            | Just like your transfers and payments, we keep all your details you give us in a secure location in which nobody can figure out your data as only we know the algorithm to see your details
                .col
                    .feature-card.shadow
                        i.far.fa-clock
                        h4.my-3 Instant Transfers
                        p.d-none.d-lg-block
                            | Encryption and decryption take milliseconds so each transfer takes a matter of seconds
